import React from "react";

function ContactForm() {
  return (
    <form class="contact-form">
      <input
        name="name"
        type="text"
        class="feedback-input"
        placeholder="Name"
      />
      <input
        name="email"
        type="text"
        class="feedback-input"
        placeholder="Email"
      />
      <textarea
        name="text"
        class="feedback-input"
        placeholder="Comment"
      ></textarea>
      <input type="submit" value="SUBMIT" />
    </form>
  );
}

export default ContactForm;
